oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Camel Rock & Roll Dance Party - 1956-05-19 - Part 2
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: CBS Rock 'N' Roll Dance Party program sponsored by Camel cigarettes, 1956-05-19 part 2. Hosted by Alan Freed with announcer Roy Rowan, starring Count Basie and his Orchestra with vocalist Joe Williams, and special guest star Bernice Gooden.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Bernice Gooden; Joe Williams; Count Basie Orchestra
